headline: Trimble (TRMB) Upgraded to Strong Buy: Here's Why
summary: Trimble (TRMB) has been upgraded to a Zacks Rank #1 (Strong Buy), reflecting growing optimism about the company's earnings prospects. This might drive the stock higher in the near term.
